## $setStatus{online|playing|Activity text}

### Message Receive, Private Message, Member Join, Member Leave, Member Ban, Reaction Add

Sets the bot status from a command. The first parameter is online, idle, or dnd. The second is watching, playing, listening, competing, or reset. The third is activity text limited to 128 characters.

